timelineItems.title: YELLOW CARD: Jermain Defoe pulls down Horst

timelineItems.comment: Foul by Jermain Defoe (Toronto FC).
David Horst (Houston Dynamo) wins a free kick in the defensive half.

timelineItems.name: Timothy Jansen
timelineItems.text: Goals in the first half, & now we are exchanging yellow cards. Please let us just put one in the net & get out of town with 3 pts #TFCLive

timelineItems.name: Wendy
timelineItems.text: I miss Gilberto very suddenly. #TFCLive

timelineItems.comment: Jermain Defoe (Toronto FC) wins a free kick in the attacking half.
Foul by A.J. Cochran (Houston Dynamo).

timelineItems.name: Darrell Lovell
timelineItems.text: Defoe with a hard foul and Horst doesn't not back down with a few shoves. Kind of funny to see Horst looking down on Defoe, who got a yellow

timelineItems.name: lau it
timelineItems.text: How is that not a yellow for the defender too? #TFCLive

timelineItems.name: Dan Riccio
timelineItems.text: Defoe misses next match after that yellow. #TFCLive

timelineItems.comment: Attempt blocked. Jonathan Osorio (Toronto FC) right footed shot from outside the box is blocked. Assisted by Dominic Oduro.
Corner,  Toronto FC. Conceded by Kofi Sarkodie.
Attempt saved. Giles Barnes (Houston Dynamo) right footed shot from the right side of the box is saved in the bottom left corner. Assisted by Will Bruin with a headed pass.

timelineItems.name: Aaron Sinukoff
timelineItems.text: Odd call there.. #TFCLive

timelineItems.name: Mitchell Tierney
timelineItems.text: With that Yellow Card Jermaine Defoe will be suspended for his next #MLS match. Are you happy they brought him on now? #TFCLive

timelineItems.comment: Foul by Nick Hagglund (Toronto FC).
Óscar García (Houston Dynamo) wins a free kick on the left wing.

timelineItems.name: Carldinho
timelineItems.text: Defoe should bang one in to show these Houston mans who they're dealing with #TFC

timelineItems.name: #LoveThisTeam?
timelineItems.text: Bend it like Bendik #TFCLive

timelineItems.name: HoustonDynamo
timelineItems.text: Minimum four minutes of stoppage time. Can the Dynamo find a winner?

timelineItems.name: Tj Llewellyn
timelineItems.text: Joe Bendik >>> Tim Howard #TFClive

timelineItems.name: MLS Insider Canada
timelineItems.text: 'Smart' yellow card for Defoe, now he can play 90 minutes against Spurs and be suspended against SKC #TFCLive

timelineItems.comment: Brad Davis (Houston Dynamo) wins a free kick on the left wing.
Foul by Nick Hagglund (Toronto FC).

timelineItems.name: Aneil Gokhale
timelineItems.text: This @torontofc match has been entertaining! Hope they can pull it out during extra time. Good intensity & chances on both sides! #TFCLive

timelineItems.comment: Second Half ends, Houston Dynamo 2, Toronto FC 2.
